snippet: A man accused of killing two Alaska State Troopers who were featured in a reality TV series has been indicted by a grand jury while two other men face banishment from their town by a tribal government over the incident, authorities said on Friday....

headline.print_headline: Man Suspected of Killing Alaska Troopers Indicted by Grand Jury
headline.main: Man Suspected of Killing Alaska Troopers Indicted by Grand Jury

lead_paragraph: A man accused of killing two Alaska State Troopers who were featured in a reality TV series has been indicted by a grand jury while two other men face banishment from their town by a tribal government over the incident, authorities said on Friday.
